      <tuv xml:lang="en"><seg>Integration services While almost all universities provide ongoing counselling and non-academic support services, as well as academic advising support, to international students, Dr. Timmons, from the University of Prince Edward Island, was surprised to see that only 47 percent of universities offer specific programs to ensure a successful experience for international students during their academic stay in Canada.</seg></tuv>
